kiɖe (Dôme)
kiɖe kɛna matʋ sɔsɔtʋ natʋyʋ siŋŋ wonuu. Tɔm piye kiɖe kɛ tɔm piye nɖɩ ɖɩtɔbʋʋ wɩlɩʋ ɛzɩ pɔlɔkɩ yaa puhuzuu kuduyuu kolaɣ taa yɔɔ yaa kuduyuu n̄ʋʋ taa yɔ. Pɛtɛ lɔbʋʋ yaa huzuu kuduyuu ŋgʋ nɛ ŋna kɔyɔ, ŋna size kʋlɔbʋtʋ taa peeɖe wɛ kulukulu yaa kuluŋgulu.


Kuduyuu ŋgʋ, kʋ-n̄ʋʋ taa peeɖe wɛɛ ɖɔɖɔ ɛzɩ payaɣ nɛ pɔtɔŋna fransɩ kʋnʋŋ taa size "elliptique" yaa "polygonal". Pɔlɔkɩ pɛtɛ lɛ, pahʋzɩ pazɩ pazɩ nɛ mbʋ payaɣna fransɩ kʋnʋŋ taa size "lanternon" yɔ. Pɩtɛ wɛtʋ taa wɛ ɛzɩ keɣye yɔ. Kiɖe kɛ cɔcɔ naŋ kuduyuu sɔsɔʋ siŋŋ kɛ Ɛsɔ kɩlaŋ laya cɔlɔ.

Pɩɩkɛ kuduyuu ŋgʋ, kɩkɛ pɩyʋ siŋŋ kɛ cɔɔcɩ yaa krɩstʋ mba hɔɔlʋʋ taa. Kuduyuŋ ɛnɛ, ɛwɛ ajɛɛ anɛ a-taa : Itaali, nɛ Caama ajɛɛ taa. Kuduyuŋ matʋ sɔsɔtʋ tʋnɛ, tuhuuwa yaa tɩkpa ɖoŋ siŋŋ kɛ ɛjaɖɛ nɖɩ payaɣ-ɖɩ size Roma tɛ Pantewɔɔ (Panthéon de Rome) yɔ ɖɩ-tɛ ɛsakuliye hɔɔlʋʋ taa.


Kajalaɣ kiɖe matʋ sɔsɔtʋ kɛ wɩsɩ ɖɩlɩyɛ ɛjaɖɛ hɔɔlʋʋ taa, kaakɛna ɖajaa sɔsɔ Filippo Brunelleschi ɖoŋ taa kɛ pɩnaɣ 1436 n̄ɩŋga taa. Ɖajaa sɔsɔ Florence tɛ ti-kiɖe ɖɔɖɔ kaakɛ kajalaɣ nɖɩ naɖɩyɛ ɖɔɖɔ. Ɖajaa sɔsɔ Louis XV n̄azɩtʋ yaa waɖɛ haʋ alɩwaatʋ taa kɛ pama Parii tɛ Panthéon (Panthéon de Paris).

